name: Mars Card 31 – Five Fish from Mars; special 'open' edition
description: To celebrate the history-making flight on a world other than Earth in April 2021, here is the 31st in a set of tradeable cards to be released by SMART | Pop Artist which features a blend of his painting ‘The Freshwater Five’ with NASA’s closeup of 'Send Your Name to Mars' chips on Perseverance Rover
